      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl142_LabelType\">You know how best to appear supportive of the current regime despite the vagaries of a shifting government.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl142_LabelType\">Galt</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl142_LabelType\">The Sense Motive DC needed for a city guard, a politician, or other governmental functionary in a large town or larger settlement to gain a hunch about your trustworthiness is 25 (instead of 20). On a failed check, you&rsquo;re seen as trustworthy regardless of the situation.</span></p>",
